casebody.data:
No. 109,

Orig.

Oklahoma et al. v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 501 U. S. 1277.]

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $14,499.45 for the period December 1, 1990, through October 31, 1991, to be paid one-third by each party.
